				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Apparently, the only class in the game allowed to mez effectively is the enchanter.  Anyone else with any kind of mez spell needs to have severe limitations on it.  Since Necromancers already have some precedence in the charm/mez department, it is only natural that they would have a higher cap on their spell than we do on ours.
<br />

<br />
Would it make logical sense that any other class would be able to summon a pet even half as effective as ours, or have a damage shield even close to ours?  Would it even make sense that ANY other class besides Cleric have heal spells effective enough to sustain an experience group?  Each class has its own special niche that no other classes should or can encroach on.
<br />

<br />
(Tongue planted firmly in cheek, ie dripping with sarcasm)</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
