				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Balance rarely includes adding abilities.  Most of the balancing that needs to be done revolves around abilities that we already have, but are rather subpar in comparison to other classes.  We could never slow, root, be efficient CC (efficient being key word), so I don't see a problem with that.
<br />

<br />
DD Damage, Pet damage, Utility are the areas where the Magician class needs major improvement.
<br />

<br />
It's not a flame or a potshot, just a simple fact.  That is most probably the way the Devs at SOE see it anyways.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Aweee, did Mister Meanie Inkie come gank you and take your spawn? Would you like a tissue? Oh you think that if you spam him for the next hour calling him every hostile word in your petty little head that you are going to upset him? Bluebie Please.</span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
